'''M. P. Ahammed''' (born 1 November 1957) is an Indian [[Businessperson|businessman]] and the [[chairman]] of Malabar Group of Companies. He is also the founder of [[Malabar Gold and Diamonds]], one of world’s largest retail jewellery groups.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.economictimes.com/slideshows/investments-markets/top-6-jewellers-who-control-indias-gold/slideshow/19827320.cms|title=Top Six Jewellers who control India's Gold.|work=Economic Times|first=|last=|date=3 May 2013}}</ref>
